#originalTopic=Creationism_Is_Wrong
 None of the things that people put forward as evidence of a god are evidence for a specific religion. Thor? Zeus? Eighty Bird Men from Krypton? There is no reason to pick just one to believe in, so I guess we should believe everything. Anyone in the market for an invisible dog? I'll sell you mine, real cheap...